cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for tagging unstructured texts with an ontology. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
